name: Hangzhou is coming
description:
Tezos is unique. 
This is the one and only protocol that is self-amending.
Its governance is democratic.
Its decentralization is real.
Its security is above every PoS protocol thanks to its language and the formal verification. 

I.e. in 2019 French army choose Tezos instead of Ethereum because they analysed that Solidity was not strong enough for them to use it. They still use Tezos and promote it to new services in the army.

Basically, everything on Ethereum would run better, faster & cheaper on Tezos.
